gomodel:SYNGO_1156  a     owl:Ontology ;
        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: In this study, Kao et al. performed subcellular fractionation of the rat brain and observed an enrichment of all synapsins, specifically synapsin 3, in the purified synaptic vesicle fraction (Fig. 5).. Experimental description: Subcellular fractions of rat cerebral cortex were obtained, and purification of synaptic vesicles and quantitative salt extraction of endogenous synapsins were performed as described." ;
        lego:modelstate   "production" ;
        dc:contributor    "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-0808-7003" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0003-1542-3498" , "https://orcid.org/0000-0002-3898-5197" ;
